97fb13d943e3a882fb89e10f","tid":286492,"uid":23096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下 會唔會比人施壓？即係有一邊好兇，唔硬吹佢foul</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n揸正黎做<br />\n<br />\n除非a贏緊b 好多球 強弱懸殊得好緊要<br />\n有喞可有可無既犯規咪唔吹<br />\n例如a禁區散到b手<br />\n反正唔影響到賽果"},{"pid":"80fbb0a34e153f0cbad9c1aaa75a3c4e1c583e24","tid":286492,"uid":23096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學屆？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 石地</blockquote><br />\n姐係盲撚球證</blockquote><br />\n冇我地呢班你口中既盲撚，你波都開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09361a4d2aeece79e5fa7b8925fd65ef1a5c6d3","tid":286492,"uid":54339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學屆？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 石地</blockquote><br />\n姐係盲撚球證</blockquote><br />\n冇我地呢班你口中既盲撚，你波都開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上過足總球證班<br />\n以前話球證盲 但事實係唔做過真係唔知有幾難睇<br />\n最簡單睇越位已簡係<br />\n你要係攻方傳波個一刻 判定所有球員有冇係越位位置 而且有冇拎波 有得益先舉旗<br />\n仲未計有球員會後上 又有係越位位置既球員墮後<br />\n勁撚難睇<br />\n<br />\n而且咩禁區手球 犯規個啲 視線俾人遮左就真係乜都睇唔到"},{"pid":"d2d6eab8a5324333e7d3817ba6d4d3bdcd383f99","tid":286492,"uid":23096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T02:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學屆？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 石地</blockquote><br />\n姐係盲撚球證</blockquote><br />\n冇我地呢班你口中既盲撚，你波都開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上過足總球證班<br />\n以前話球證盲 但事實係唔做過真係唔知有幾難睇<br />\n最簡單睇越位已簡係<br />\n你要係攻方傳波個一刻 判定所有球員有冇係越位位置 而且有冇拎波 有得益先舉旗<br />\n仲未計有球員會後上 又有係越位位置既球員墮後<br />\n勁撚難睇<br />\n<br />\n而且咩禁區手球 犯規個啲 視線俾人遮左就真係乜都睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n岩呀<br />\n永遠踢個啲睇個啲都以為好易睇<br />\n其實好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a3ea592e8c47c3b77590644f064326f4b9bb1a","tid":286492,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:06:37.000Z","msg":"有冇即場發現自己吹錯咗<br />\n但死撐照吹"},{"pid":"1be423c59bb6d25b6930d00a19a859291004bf44","tid":286492,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T03:23:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學屆？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 石地</blockquote><br />\n姐係盲撚球證</blockquote><br />\n冇我地呢班你口中既盲撚，你波都開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上過足總球證班<br />\n以前話球證盲 但事實係唔做過真係唔知有幾難睇<br />\n最簡單睇越位已簡係<br />\n你要係攻方傳波個一刻 判定所有球員有冇係越位位置 而且有冇拎波 有得益先舉旗<br />\n仲未計有球員會後上 又有係越位位置既球員墮後<br />\n勁撚難睇<br />\n<br />\n而且咩禁區手球 犯規個啲 視線俾人遮左就真係乜都睇唔到</blockquote><br />\n岩呀<br />\n永遠踢個啲睇個啲都以為好易睇<br />\n其實好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果吹正式（一正兩副）旁證係同last 2防守球員（越位線）平排㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n讀書時上過足總班"},{"pid":"b66824cbe7b30021f45b2d13882a17d26b9d37c5","tid":286492,"uid":23096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇即場發現自己吹錯咗<br />\n但死撐照吹</blockquote><br />\n界外球個啲有錯咪改<br />\n但犯規錯左點都要死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e6f41e3aa51e57f149a2d77c14ae4fe8b1e869","tid":286492,"uid":26422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"有時石場屌鳩啲球證吹錯其實佢地真係會驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會吹番偏向番自己嗰邊"},{"pid":"7d4b5d40afb9d0621159563697465b6a3626208f","tid":286492,"uid":26422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇即場發現自己吹錯咗<br />\n但死撐照吹</blockquote><br />\n界外球個啲有錯咪改<br />\n但犯規錯左點都要死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n界外球見到吹嗰隊都褪開 九成都會吹番另一面波"},{"pid":"cb0ac98223f3e040a2247efeea01db9acc7a11f8","tid":286492,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點樣先可以係世界盃執法？</blockquote><br />\n考到國際頂級既球證牌卦</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過有朝一日可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18aa62d80e29997659a1ec5f7b05534e38fdc1b7","tid":286492,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:10:43.000Z","msg":"有冇拍過Gigi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ee8fffab689d7f3c12e4c16a0d4f945649e5e7","tid":286492,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"有冇試過俾球員恐嚇？<br />\n有冇試過俾人打"},{"pid":"af361f9b1d8f86f03c0d71e348f3e8b86784869d","tid":286492,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:27:04.000Z","msg":"260一場 90分鐘不停跑 <br />\n真係你做埋我果份"},{"pid":"99c744ed981c6c43d0a3712e3119ff328346ac83","tid":286492,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>260一場 90分鐘不停跑 <br />\n真係你做埋我果份</blockquote><br />\n石地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3bbe2c6a92d9f1044a70b3099e2add2e5b5260","tid":286492,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"有冇試過讚個啲球員好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978d706a11f5cbfb2bc34569332ac8137b841625","tid":286492,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過讚個啲球員好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知啲球證係咪純粹出於禮貌先會讚球員好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半年前比球證讚我好波開心到而家"},{"pid":"8734fa78e2d2e8aa2a83c5dbe25c9429ae080ed7","tid":286492,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇試過讚個啲球員好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想知啲球證係咪純粹出於禮貌先會讚球員好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半年前比球證讚我好波開心到而家</blockquote><br />\n我自己試過一次 我本身對波啲人唔係好識踢波 主要都係玩籃球 有一次對排榜首嘅球隊  強弱懸殊 結果我哋全場死守都贏3比0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住個球定同我哋講: 你哋咁樣都贏到3比0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6f2078f935e1d722de9d8e14bb5e17ba294756","tid":286492,"uid":37798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"如果你+雙方球員都冇共同語言咁點溝通?"},{"pid":"b99f8b5fbd08a65cd6fca310ca5341c148ae068e","tid":286492,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"石地球證全部垃圾<br />\n屌你老母上次話要比球證費<br />\n咁大家出晒去準備開波<br />\n你老母條傻閪球證過黎話比錢先<br />\n我好聲好氣問半場先得唔得 冇散紙<br />\n條撚樣勁撚串話唔比錢唔開波<br />\n正一大種乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944c46dcc74b2fb892a615f7fb06f39c7c9ec226","tid":286492,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"想做黑哨有冇辦法搭路？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要一場一千以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06841561dabdf034f0e0a35538d2b91ed492db68","tid":286492,"uid":92072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"覺爺係咪你偶像"}]}